          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "As Columbia <a href=\"https://www.columbiaspectator.com/news/2023/10/04/shafik-inaugurated-as-20th-university-president-in-ceremony-that-draws-hundreds-of-protestors/\">celebrated</a> the inauguration of Minouche Shafik on October 4, members of Sunrise held a painted sign that read in bold letters, “Shafik: in. Fossil fuels: out.”"
